  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    Ingestor

    public interface IngestorInterface
    This interface is used as a template for data ingestion on cloud platforms. All parameters for all methods are interfaces, such that users may define their own implementations for use, while still using the Tools.Importer base class to upload
